10 cell /base exch def
{ base cell-get dup 20 ge { pop 1 0 div } if } cell-computed /bad exch def
bad cell-get pop                            % initial eval succeeds (10 < 20)
bad { pop pop } watch
{ { 20 base cell-set } batch } try /div-by-zero eq  (error: batch-fire recompute error) rt-ok  clear

