% SECTION 157: FUZZ -- cell-transduce xf-drop
% =================================================================

[10 20 30 40 50] cell /src exch def
src 2 xf-drop cell-transduce /dropped exch def
dropped cell-get [30 40 50] deep-eq       (cell-transduce: xf-drop) rt-ok  clear

